{"id": "1186383905826283631", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "441584098381660192", "author_name": "blackmarimo", "author_bot": false, "content": "可以試試這樣...\n\n超維主要靠   莉茲疊毒\n注意 超維空間，算力的利用\n\n血肉主要靠  雷婭、菲因特  \n不停的回血+死亡抵抗+疊力量\n靠著希洛不停的持續打擊，最後蘿坦的 覺醒+狂氣爆發 收尾\nP.S ：希洛/蘿坦，擇一 在命盤中加入 「切割與傷害」，提高容錯率", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T19:06:05.096000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1186328202730287236"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1186383905138421940", "filename": "Screenshot_20231219-025705.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 161188, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1131839874132090890/1186383905138421940/Screenshot_20231219-025705.jpg?ex=6a378d5c&is=6a363bdc&hm=f66afb00f968ec34a0b0b2b2f01dc003955ed745eed92f46778a5b07c470d1a7&"}, {"id": "1186383905603997807", "filename": "Screenshot_20231219-025711.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 178264, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1131839874132090890/1186383905603997807/Screenshot_20231219-025711.jpg?ex=6a378d5d&is=6a363bdd&hm=8df3a844b7c760d24ea58195864544d2f98bdd40e827ceb3bef1a35a09eb5e58&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1186330048349880390", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186386287809265664", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 19, "author_id": "441584098381660192", "author_name": "blackmarimo", "author_bot": false, "content": "超維隊\n需要額外注意 莉茲 手牌的留存\n\n存牌時：艾瑞卡的 X費 機能超載 是  常用的好幫手\n\n牌多、即將進入超維回合時：朵爾的「等價交換」、溫柯爾的「精神重建（非躍遷）」\n都會是你很好的選擇", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T19:15:33.005000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1186383905826283631", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
